    source: "Hacker News Discussion, Jul 2025",
    insight: "Hallucinations are inevitable at scale",
    icon: "ðŸŽ²"
  },
  {
    quote: "1 in 10 times it fails, nearly always because the demo gods got involved. LLMs are probabilisticâ€”unreliability is fundamental to the architecture.",
    source: "HN discussion on AI tool reliability",
    insight: "Stochastic systems have stochastic failures",
